  "detailed_description": "Flowing rivers, rushing waterfalls, unexplored towering trees...<br />\r\nNitori's adventure begins here and now!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA 3D action game with 5 stages in total!<br />\r\nExplore the world alongside the energetic kappa Nitori!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this game, you progress by gathering cucumbers<br />\r\nand Memories scattered around each of its maps.<br />\r\nCucumbers are used to gain skills, increase max HP,<br />\r\nunlock shortcuts, and more, while Memories are used<br />\r\nfor things like unlocking new maps.",
  "about_the_game": "Flowing rivers, rushing waterfalls, unexplored towering trees...<br />\r\nNitori's adventure begins here and now!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA 3D action game with 5 stages in total!<br />\r\nExplore the world alongside the energetic kappa Nitori!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this game, you progress by gathering cucumbers<br />\r\nand Memories scattered around each of its maps.<br />\r\nCucumbers are used to gain skills, increase max HP,<br />\r\nunlock shortcuts, and more, while Memories are used<br />\r\nfor things like unlocking new maps.",
